# Link to this sectionRoboflow 100 データセット#

Roboflow 100, sponsored by [Intel](https://www.intel.com/), is a groundbreaking [object detection](/ja/tasks/detect) benchmark dataset. It includes 100 diverse datasets. This benchmark is specifically designed to test the adaptability of [computer vision](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/computer-vision-cv) models, like [Ultralytics YOLO models](/ja/models/yolo26), to various domains, including healthcare, aerial imagery, and video games.

